<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Reset Your Password - Houmti</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Helvetica', Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f9fafb;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      color: #333333;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 12px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #0052cc;
      color: #ffffff;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 30px 20px;
      font-size: 26px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .body {
      padding: 30px 20px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    .code-container {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 30px 0;
    }
    .code {
      font-size: 34px;
      font-weight: bold;
      letter-spacing: 8px;
      color: #0052cc;
      background-color: #e6f0ff;
      padding: 15px 25px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      display: inline-block;
    }
    .warning {
      margin-top: 25px;
      padding: 15px;
      background-color: #fff4e5;
      border-left: 4px solid #ffa726;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #8a6d3b;
    }
    .footer {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #888888;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .footer a {
      color: #0052cc;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    p {
      margin: 15px 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">

```
<div class="header">
  Password Reset Request
</div>

<div class="body">
  <p>Hello {{ name }},</p>

  <p>We received a request to reset your Houmti account password.</p>

  <p>Use the verification code below to proceed:</p>

  <div class="code-container">
    <div class="code">{{ code }}</div>
  </div>

  <p>This code is valid for <strong>10 minutes</strong>.</p>

  <div class="warning">
    If you didn’t request this password reset, you can safely ignore this email. Your account will remain secure.
  </div>

  <p>For security reasons, never share this code with anyone.</p>

  <p>Best regards,<br>The Houmti Team</p>
</div>

<div class="footer">
  Houmti App – Your smart companion<br>
  <a href="https://houmti.app">houmti.app</a>
</div>
```

  </div>
</body>
</html>
